data.name: 月刊少女野崎くん 15 [Gekkan Shoujo Nozaki-kun 15]
data.publisher: スクウェア・エニックス
data.introducing: She is a Japanese manga artist known for creating The Magic Touch and Oresama Teacher which have both been serialized on the Hana to Yume magazine./nTsubaki began drawing manga in her first year of high school. She was soon selected to be in the top 10 of Hana to Yume Mangaka Course, and subsequently won the Big Challenge contest.
